sources.description:
Christmas Eve 1944.  Two young, soldiers, one American, and one German, have been lost in the woods after being separated from their units. As the night passes, the enemies must confront their own humanity if they are to survive.

2024.  Stars: Judith Feingold, Preston Mead, Cj Voteur
